TEMPO_HCHO_L3_V04_20250912T210435Z_S012_.summary: Formaldehyde Level 3 files provide trace gas information on a regular grid covering the TEMPO field of regard for nominal TEMPO observations. Level 3 files are derived by combining information from all Level 2 files constituting a TEMPO East-West scan cycle. The files are provided in netCDF4 format, and contain information on formaldehyde vertical columns, ancillary data used in air mass factor calculations and reference sector or de-striping corrections, and retrieval quality flags. The re-gridding algorithm uses an area-weighted approach.
TEMPO_HCHO_L3_V04_20250912T210435Z_S012_.title: TEMPO Level 3 formaldehyde product
